{"info": {"author": "Leif Denby", "author_email": "leif@denby.eu", "bugtrack_url": null, "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 2 - Pre-Alpha", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Natural Language :: English", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.5", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.6", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.7", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.8"], "description": "# Download tool for NASA WorldView\n\n![](docs/GOES_2020-01-28T16:10:00+00:00.png)\n\n[![Build\nStatus](https://travis-ci.com/leifdenby/worldview_dl.svg?branch=master)](https://travis-ci.com/leifdenby/worldview_dl)\n\n## Installation\n\n```bash\n> pip install worldview_dl\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nYou may either download using the command line cli:\n\n```bash\nusage: cli.py [-h] [--layers LAYERS [LAYERS ...]] [--image_type IMAGE_TYPE]\n              [--resolution RESOLUTION] [--end-time END_TIME]\n              time bbox\n```\n\nfor example\n\n```bash\n> python -m worldview_dl.cli \"2020-01-28 16:20\" 10.,-60.,15.,-50. --image_type png\n```\n\nOr with the python package\n\n```python\nfrom worldview_dl import download_image\nimport datetime\nimport pytz\n\nt_now = datetime.datetime.now().replace(tzinfo=pytz.utc)\nt = t_now - datetime.timedelta(hours=2)\n\ndownload_image(\n    fn=\"GOES_test.png\",\n    time=t,\n    bbox=[10.,-60.,15.,-50.],\n    layers=['GOES-East_ABI_Band2_Red_Visible_1km', 'Reference_Labels'],\n    image_format=\"png\",\n    resolution=0.01,\n)\n```", "description_content_type": "text/markdown", "docs_url": null, "download_url": "", "downloads": {"last_day": -1, "last_month": -1, "last_week": -1}, "home_page": "https://github.com/leifdenby/worldview_dl", "keywords": "worldview_dl", "license": "MIT license", "maintainer": "", "maintainer_email": "", "name": "worldview-dl", "package_url": "https://pypi.org/project/worldview-dl/", "platform": "", "project_url": "https://pypi.org/project/worldview-dl/", "project_urls": {"Homepage": "https://github.com/leifdenby/worldview_dl"}, "release_url": "https://pypi.org/project/worldview-dl/0.2.0/", "requires_dist": null, "requires_python": ">=3.5", "summary": "Download utility for NASA WorldView", "version": "0.2.0", "yanked": false, "html_description": "<div class=\"project-description\">\n            <h1>Download tool for NASA WorldView</h1>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://warehouse-camo.ingress.cmh1.psfhosted.org/2569b6aa0c07beb2121ae3698df20c29906cb1c2/646f63732f474f45535f323032302d30312d32385431363a31303a30302b30303a30302e706e67\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://travis-ci.com/leifdenby/worldview_dl\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"Build Status\" src=\"https://warehouse-camo.ingress.cmh1.psfhosted.org/3dc9a642eaec07b147a461ba5f7b5278159bf1b6/68747470733a2f2f7472617669732d63692e636f6d2f6c65696664656e62792f776f726c64766965775f646c2e7376673f6272616e63683d6d6173746572\"></a></p>\n<h2>Installation</h2>\n<pre>&gt; pip install worldview_dl\n</pre>\n<h2>Usage</h2>\n<p>You may either download using the command line cli:</p>\n<pre>usage: cli.py <span class=\"o\">[</span>-h<span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span>--layers LAYERS <span class=\"o\">[</span>LAYERS ...<span class=\"o\">]]</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span>--image_type IMAGE_TYPE<span class=\"o\">]</span>\n              <span class=\"o\">[</span>--resolution RESOLUTION<span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span>--end-time END_TIME<span class=\"o\">]</span>\n              <span class=\"nb\">time</span> bbox\n</pre>\n<p>for example</p>\n<pre>&gt; python -m worldview_dl.cli <span class=\"s2\">\"2020-01-28 16:20\"</span> <span class=\"m\">10</span>.,-60.,15.,-50. --image_type png\n</pre>\n<p>Or with the python package</p>\n<pre><span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">worldview_dl</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">download_image</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"nn\">datetime</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"nn\">pytz</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">t_now</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">datetime</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">datetime</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">now</span><span class=\"p\">()</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">replace</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">tzinfo</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">pytz</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">utc</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">t</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">t_now</span> <span class=\"o\">-</span> <span class=\"n\">datetime</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">timedelta</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">hours</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">download_image</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">fn</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">\"GOES_test.png\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">time</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">t</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">bbox</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"mf\">10.</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mf\">60.</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mf\">15.</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mf\">50.</span><span class=\"p\">],</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">layers</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"s1\">'GOES-East_ABI_Band2_Red_Visible_1km'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"s1\">'Reference_Labels'</span><span class=\"p\">],</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">image_format</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">\"png\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">resolution</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"mf\">0.01</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</pre>\n\n          </div>"}, "last_serial": 6538758, "releases": {"0.1.0": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "ddfad558c6c3dbf01169752c0500015b", "sha256": "572573aa64ea520edb3f6bdb9e84ef481dfdcfdca5c9df89ff56fb143355921a"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "worldview_dl-0.1.0.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "ddfad558c6c3dbf01169752c0500015b", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": ">=3.5", "size": 484432, "upload_time": "2020-01-29T15:32:35", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2020-01-29T15:32:35.696398Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/f8/87/13d0834c8195a4239f2397c45685d97adce6d6a3f0b88ace4f67848d22ae/worldview_dl-0.1.0.tar.gz", "yanked": false}], "0.2.0": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "2c08676b4b621c22f546f9f2c477c0a6", "sha256": "bce83f21ab582ba46c0500d45483d9e90cea33447c764fb097a94622ccc5fa8e"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "worldview_dl-0.2.0.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "2c08676b4b621c22f546f9f2c477c0a6", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": ">=3.5", "size": 484246, "upload_time": "2020-01-29T16:06:09", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2020-01-29T16:06:09.823977Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/2a/51/32640fcbcbe05df486467d2c4551e5b7280091c27a563b70c3397413aa5d/worldview_dl-0.2.0.tar.gz", "yanked": false}]}, "urls": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "2c08676b4b621c22f546f9f2c477c0a6", "sha256": "bce83f21ab582ba46c0500d45483d9e90cea33447c764fb097a94622ccc5fa8e"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "worldview_dl-0.2.0.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "2c08676b4b621c22f546f9f2c477c0a6", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": ">=3.5", "size": 484246, "upload_time": "2020-01-29T16:06:09", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2020-01-29T16:06:09.823977Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/2a/51/32640fcbcbe05df486467d2c4551e5b7280091c2